this weekend was so perfect :) friday night i slept at ericas with the girls, much needed, very much! we stopped by jcal's, had a couple drinks. it was fun, im glad matt came for a little while! saturday night matt didnt feel to good so i stayed at his house for a good 9 hours. i swear i can never get tired of him. ahh, im in love :) and today me and matt went out for lunch and then hit marshalls, t.jj's, barnes and nobel, and the paper store. i missed out on church this morning, totally forgot and woke up at 10:30 to butlas text. im an idiot! mid-terms start tomorrow, shouldnt be to too bad. eh, they will be over before we know it. the end.
today was absolutely WONDERFUL :) i am so in love.

i love matt more than anything in this world and i dont ever want to loose him especially because of my parents. this is rediculous shit that all needs to stop. it needs to stop NOW! i fucked up, period. end of story. get over it, move on, we all did and you can too! everything in the last week has been shit. it was all so good and now its shit. fuck

this new year is starting off SHITTY.

help.

2005 is gone. so much happened. it seemed never ending and im so glad that everything that did happen happened. no regrets on anything! i found out a lot of things, i got a new crew of friends that i love to death and i have matt, the one boy that means the absolute world to me. i love you matt! gawd, this year was an unforgetable one! there are a select few that i miss more than anything. boy did we have a good time together. ill never forget any of it. i wish it could all go back but for some reason that hasnt happened yet and im not sure how its gunna all work out. im looking forwad to this year and nothings gunna bring me down. in other news, last night was such a good time! i missed butla and ash and dicer. we were supposed to meat up but that kinda fell through :\ me and matt and beano and drew and chris and tom and dolla and alyssa and felicia watched that ball drop like there was no tomorrow! haha. that was an intresting night let me tell you, pure fun! thats all i got bitches. 2006, here we come ;)
